Ranger Help for: ranhelp
=========================

SYNTAX:      ranhelp [topic]
             rh [topic]
USAGE:       Anywhere

SUMMARY:
This command accesses the Ranger guild help system. Type 'ranhelp' or
'rh' followed by a topic to view help on that subject. Without a topic,
it displays a list of available help categories. This is the same as
the 'rhelp' command.

EXAMPLES:
  ranhelp skills     - View help on Ranger skills
  rh archery         - View help on archery
  rh general         - View general guild overview
